# String unpacker
This program helps you to unpack coded string to their normal form.

## Examples
* Ex. 1
  * a1b2c3
  * abbccc
* Ex. 2
  * a3B2c1
  * aaaBBc
* Ex. 3
  * z17E17n5i1E15t3j14f4Q13D7p8Z19h1x8k11l5T2C18S7v17I10h1k15B12K4R6X5v5K8c3i17T13F8R15D9
  *
